 p\u00e5 sykehjemmet. N\u00e5 krysser vi fingrene for at han klarer seg, sier Due Winsjansen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "dffb33e1331509ca96aa83dddcc0bf03a4a1909397a80ae3ecd651cac7f7d065"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T08:51:58.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Magne Sand\u00f8y (77) ligger i kunstig koma p\u00e5 St. Olavs Hospital etter frontkollisjonen i Rissa."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article3288617.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ols%C3%B8y%20krasj%20ok.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/18a3f23a942fa1bd92186e99781b7d2b2f13d843.jpg?595fc795"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Kjent maler alvorlig skadd i frontkollisjon -adressa.no", "Fikk kulturpris i 1976", "Hadde v\u00e6rt p\u00e5 bes\u00f8k i Trondheim"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "18a3f23a942fa1bd92186e99781b7d2b2f13d843"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["frontkollisjon", "ulykken", "kunstig koma", "kunstig", "bes\u00f8k", "koma", "trondheim", "alvorlig", "malt"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["olavs hospital", "r\u00e5kv\u00e5g", "anna due winsjansen", "ols\u00f8ykrysset", "due winsjansen", "rissamartnan", "norsk", "adressa", "st. olavs hospital"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim", "nord-tr\u00f8ndelag", "rissa"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, 